Class ExpressionCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataProcessing.ExpressionCalculator

  • public final class ExpressionCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    Static utility class responsible for calculating expressions based on an input string. The class is strictly for utility and not be be instantiated.
